    <note>He(2) Wan [686] Zhizhong's [8053] brother. Hong Kuo, WJ, 76.5b has Zhizhong as Xiang(2) Yunzhong's [17847] (q.v.) father-in-law. Yunzhong's wife was enfeoffed Weiguo furen and was the aunt of the wife of Xiang(2) Zhongkan [3352], brother of Xiang(2) Bofen [706]. Zhongkan's wife was the granddaughter of He(2) Wan. Wan could be a cousin, but I am identifying him as an elder brother of Zhizhong. XCB, 293.1a, 5b, 294.11b, 298.4a, 391.11b, 11b (n.), 406.6b; SHY:ZG, 66.6b; Zhejiang TZ, 123.27b. CBD, 2, 1261.</note>
